Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:59.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}主炮：37mm炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:59.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}追獵者
